PreviewShellMac(8)          System Manager's Manual         PreviewShellMac(8)

NAME
     PreviewShellMac – Xcode Previews agent

DESCRIPTION
     PreviewShellMac is the agent for Xcode Previews.

     There are no configuration options to PreviewShellMac, and users should
     not run PreviewShellMac manually.

